name: Mitch McConnell
summary: Mitch McConnell, the Republican leader in the Senate, has denounced the MAGA movement and former President Donald Trump, stating that Reagan "wouldn't recognize" Trump's GOP. McConnell has also expressed support for Jack Smith's investigation into the January 6th Capitol attack, suggesting he believes Trump should be held accountable. A biography of McConnell portrays him as both critical of Trump and ambitious for power. Despite his distaste for Trump, McConnell has praised former Speaker of the House Nancy Pelosi, indicating a willingness to work across party lines. Recent allegations suggest that TikTok considered using Kentucky creators to influence McConnell's decisions. McConnell has also predicted that the upcoming presidential election will be tightly contested.
